<br>
True DPS is how much damage can you do in a second (or tick).  We do rule that, don't we?  I mean, take the last third of a battle and calculate average damage per tick.  That is all we can ask.  We might not always be what is needed, but when we are, there is no real substitute.<br>
<br>
I know I have not yet come into my real power, but at 45 I have seen a great increase over the past 10 levels.  I look forward to 49 and then the 50s increments.<br>
<br>
Some people will never really get it, and we might benefit from some tweaking, but I think we do pretty well for what we are expected to do:  end fights fast.<br>
<br>
Plus, let me see the monk/warrior/rogue quad for exp when he does not feel like grouping. <p><font face=impact>

